      "layout": "The page primarily uses a max-width contained layout, though the hero section often stretches full-bleed. The hero features a large, impactful centered headline against a colored background, sometimes split with a visual element. Section rhythm is generally consistent with substantial vertical spacing (48px section gap). Content is arranged in alternating text-left/image-right or centered stacks. Card-like containers, when present, utilize the distinct 'pill' shape. Navigation is handled by a minimal top bar, with elements pushed to the far corners.",
